    "name": "Evil is Back",
    "steam_appid": 2363930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/253a4ec2873eea59d608681b2ee61c7f.avif?t=1681497161\" width=590 height=279 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/f472395079611a60afaa31b3d9cbffef.avif?t=1681497161\" width=590 height=116 /></span><br><br><strong>&quot;Evil is Back&quot;</strong> is a retelling of the movies <strong>&quot;Evil Dead 1 and 2&quot;</strong>... With everything a low budget short film should have. For fans of 80's trash horror movies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/3d699ee6b5a32571889d214c815a2c09.poster.avif?t=1681497161\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/3d699ee6b5a32571889d214c815a2c09.webm?t=1681497161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/3d699ee6b5a32571889d214c815a2c09.mp4?t=1681497161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SYNOPSIS</h2>Scott and his friends are going to spend the weekend in a cabin in the woods and isolated from the city.<br>Upon finding a very old book and accidentally reciting some words... The portal to the world of the dead opens, bringing death and destruction to all who are there.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2>Shooter with combat and survival elements. Using a sawed-off shotgun and a chainsaw to eliminate grotesque creatures. A few more average puzzles to solve.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/6644fa1bc2317abe90701c4fccdfbc7b.poster.avif?t=1681497161\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/6644fa1bc2317abe90701c4fccdfbc7b.webm?t=1681497161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/6644fa1bc2317abe90701c4fccdfbc7b.mp4?t=1681497161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HAND OR CHAINSAW?</h2>Without a doubt the best part of every &quot;Evil Dead&quot; movie is when &quot;Ash Williams&quot; loses his hand and uses a chainsaw instead. We decided to be as faithful as possible to the original work.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/59e8d526da16391079e9c96adbfaa616.poster.avif?t=1681497161\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/59e8d526da16391079e9c96adbfaa616.webm?t=1681497161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/59e8d526da16391079e9c96adbfaa616.mp4?t=1681497161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT GAME</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>CAMERA: </strong>First-person.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>CONTROL: </strong>Mouse and Keyboard only.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>GRAPHICS: </strong>Triple-b game, graphics inspired by 80's horror movies.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>DURATION: </strong>It depends a lot on the type of player, but it's not very long (30 to 60 minutes).</li></ul><br>...A lot...a lot...a lot of blood! strange enemies and an even stranger boss!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/9f9cb1e2c5c4864e6f0d8fed0e5cebe8.poster.avif?t=1681497161\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/9f9cb1e2c5c4864e6f0d8fed0e5cebe8.webm?t=1681497161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/9f9cb1e2c5c4864e6f0d8fed0e5cebe8.mp4?t=1681497161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>...Typical scenes from 80's trash movies...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/1c61262829c03d04303e8017ea5d5910.poster.avif?t=1681497161\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/1c61262829c03d04303e8017ea5d5910.webm?t=1681497161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/1c61262829c03d04303e8017ea5d5910.mp4?t=1681497161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>...The book of death... capable of opening the portal to the world of the dead...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/a2c14d34bd67b36de616db34f0f55702.avif?t=1681497161\" width=590 height=300 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363930/extras/62efa691071d10dbdf82aa2c918072f7.avif?t=1681497161\" width=590 height=116 /></span>",
